    "description": "IDflex V is a Cryptographic Module based on the Athena OS755 Java Card smart card operating system with 72KB of EEPROM. IDflex V is compliant with the latest Java Card 2.2.2 and GlobalPlatform 2.1.1 specifications and is validated to FIPS 140-2 Level 3. IDflex V supports FIPS approved DRBG, SHA-1 and all SHA-2, TDES, AES, RSA, ECDSA and ECC CDC, and RSA and ECC key generation. IDflex V exposes PKI and Biometric APIs and is designed for high-performance government and enterprise smart card applications.",
